item.title: CVE-2023-33976|2024-08-01T20:14:02.779Z -- tensorflow -- tensorflow
item.description: TensorFlow is an end-to-end open source platform for machine learning. `array_ops.upper_bound` causes a segfault when not given a rank 2 tensor. The fix will be included in TensorFlow 2.13 and will also cherrypick this commit on TensorFlow 2.12.
